WEBVTT

00:00:00.783 --> 00:00:02.631
Danas

00:00:02.631 --> 00:00:04.562
jedna zbunjena žena je primetila

00:00:04.562 --> 00:00:06.943
školjku u kojoj moja duša živi

00:00:06.943 --> 00:00:08.881
I izjavila je da sam

00:00:08.881 --> 00:00:12.750
"razgovetna"

00:00:12.750 --> 00:00:14.283
Što znači da kad su u pitanju

00:00:14.283 --> 00:00:15.950
dikcija i izgovor

00:00:15.950 --> 00:00:17.450
Ja o tome i ne razmišljam

00:00:17.450 --> 00:00:20.509
Jer ja sam "razgovetna"

00:00:20.509 --> 00:00:22.809
Kada moj profesor postavi pitanje

00:00:22.809 --> 00:00:24.742
A ja odgovoram sa konotacijom

00:00:24.742 --> 00:00:26.750
urbanizovanog predloga

00:00:26.750 --> 00:00:28.180
Nema pogrešno usmerenih namera

00:00:28.180 --> 00:00:29.158
Obratite pažnju

00:00:29.158 --> 00:00:31.700
Jer ja sam "razgovetna"